            <div class="col-lg-7 info">
              <p>We offer a variety of commercial waterproofing services.</p>
              <ul>
                <li><b>Sheet-Applied</b> - Our sheet-applied waterproofing membranes offer supreme waterproofing protection for a variety of applications.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Hot-Applied</b> - Our hot-applied rubberized asphalt waterproofing membrane provides a  combination of superb toughness and low-temperature flexibility. Its balanced mixture effectively prevents degradation of the rubber contents via overheating, and it offers extremely low absorbtion and vapor permeability.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Cold-Applied</b> - Our cold-applied single-component waterproofing compound does has a low VOC content, low odor and it does not freeze or crack in extreme cold nor degrade at high temperatures.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Blind-Side</b> - We provide blind-side waterproofing solutions at a variety of high-density job-sites where access to the positive side is impossible. Our blindside applications are designed to eliminate moisture migration into the structure, and their high level of maintainability make them an effective barrier against toxic contaminants like radon and methane that may enter a structure through cracks.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Cementitious</b> - We provide a variety of cementitious waterproofing services. Our cementitious applications are highly durable water barriers that protect buildings from dampeness and moisture damage.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Bentonite</b> - Bentonite membranes are highly expandible and flexible, and they become virtually impermeable to water and most chemicals.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <b>Vegetative</b> - We apply liquid membranes to create a durable monolithic waterproofing component within a green roof system that are able to withstand water indefinitely and can be sprayed to any thickness in one coat.
                </li>
              </ul>
